Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:05.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｴﾙ)人を正して\Nお母さんを取り戻す…｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I will correct mankind and take back my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが 僕の使命…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅ･ﾄﾞﾗﾝｺﾞ)うりゃあ～！ はあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:16.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾘｵｽ17世)神は この戦争に\Nお前の子供を利用するだろう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods will likely use your child in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If your child joins them, he will die as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:19.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦えば お前の子供も死ぬ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it. Don't pick on Jeanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:22.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ！\Nジャンヌさんをいじめるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:24.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変わらないな お前は｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What do you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何！ なんなのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you dance with me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:30.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また踊ってくれるか？\Nはっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:38.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(看守)はぁ はぁ はぁ…｡\N≫タッタッタッ(足音)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.77,0:00:48.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)助かった 感謝する｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would've imagined you'd be\Nwith the saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:52.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)まさか 聖女様が一緒だとは\N思わなかったわ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am no longer a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:55.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)もう聖女ではない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita, you always show up\Nright when I need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:58.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リタって いつも\Nピンチなときに来てくれるね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:02.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫ピィーッ！ ピィーッ！(笛の音)\N(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)急ごう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage of Bahamut
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:39.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾞﾌﾞﾘｴﾙ)過去\N我々と人間の関係は良好でした｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we had a favorable relationship with mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:43.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１０年前の\Nバハムートによる悲劇の際は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,During the Bahamut catastrophe\N10 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:46.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いに手を取り\N多大な犠牲を払って➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we took each other by the hand,\Nand made heavy sacrifices
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:50.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界を守り抜きました｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to successfully defend the world\Nfrom oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:55.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,にもかかわらず 人間たちは\N信仰心を失い 神の不要を説き➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite this,\Nmankind lost its way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,claiming it no longer needed the gods.\NMen attacked our shrines,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:03:01.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,挙句の果てに 我々の神殿を襲い\N神を殺害するまでに至りました｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and even dared to kill\Nour brothers and sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:06.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らが 自らの過ちに気付くまで\N我々は この横暴に➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we simply suffer this oppression in silence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,until mankind realizes its mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:10.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,静かに\N耐え続けるべきなのでしょうか？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:15.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,否｡ これ以上 人間たちの横暴を\N許すことはできません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We can no longer forgive mankind's\Ndomineering ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We must admonish those\Nwho have wronged us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神々を侮辱した者たちに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々の力を\N思い知らせてやるのです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:31.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺された同胞の無念を晴らし\N世界の秩序を取り戻すのです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We must avenge our fallen comrades\Nand restore balance to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:55.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)ガブリエル様\Nエルの力は まだ未知数です｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,El's powers are still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:58.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このような戦に\N果たして耐えられるか…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he withstand this war?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:03.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心配には及びません｡\Nエルが 人の力を封印したのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,El has shown to be capable of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:08.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度も証明されています｡\N(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)ですが…｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,stripping the humans of their powers\Non multiple occasions. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるしかないのです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(指揮官)空挺隊 行け！ 行け～！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Air brigade! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:38.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(指揮官)\N地上兵は 投擲車両の準備をせよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ground forces, prepare the ballistic weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:40.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(指揮官)\N兵の数を正面に集中させろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate our forces to the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:43.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(指揮官)\Nゴーレムの配置を急がせろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the golems in position!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:46.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(一同)シャリオスは死ね～！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Charioce shall die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:50.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王宮の兵は全滅しろ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The royal capital's soldiers shall be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:53.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(肉屋の妻)ほんとに 戦争するなら\Nよそでやってほしいね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're going to make war,\NI'd wish they'd do it somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(肉屋の主人)\Nうるせぇ！ とっとと逃げねぇと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! We gotta get out of here\Nbefore all hell breaks loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦が始まっちまうぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:11.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)この戦で\N俺たちの真価が問われますね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle will give us the chance\Nto prove our worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)神と戦うことに\Nお前は 何も感じないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Does fighting the gods\Nnot give you any pause?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)\Nえっ？ だったら何なんすか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:21.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく カイザル団長みたいなこと\N言わないでくださいよ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, please don't go all\NCaptain Kaisar on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,宣戦布告してきたのは\N神なんですから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods are the ones who declared war on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるっきゃないでしょ｡ ん？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't back down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお～ お前ら ご苦労｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do a good job guarding our flanks, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後方支援 しっかりやれよ～｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:36.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾌﾞｴﾙ)俺たちが前線だ｡\Nはあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be the ones on the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:39.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾌﾞｴﾙ)\N人間様は 安全な所で見物してろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You precious humans\Ncan watch us from safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:41.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:44.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾌﾞｴﾙ)グルル…｡\Nうっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:47.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾌﾞｴﾙ)\Nお前たちの王が決めたことだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what your king decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:54.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)\Nな な… 何なんすか あの態度｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What was with his attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dias, teach him some manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:56.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ディアスさん\Nやっちゃってくださいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(看守)こっちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:14.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふんっ んっ んん～ んっ！ あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うげっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)こっち｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(看守)撃て 撃て～！ 撃て～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)うっ！\Nジャンヌさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんにゃろ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴン！\N(一同)うわっ ああ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:47.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)ニーナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで足止めしとくから\N先に行って｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead, I'll hold them off here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)大丈夫？\Nすぐ追いつける｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it won't take me long\Nto catch up to you. I'm fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 足速いから｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)行きましょう｡\N(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)むちゃはするな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:04.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃあ～ こいや！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上行くと\Nニーナが分からなくなっちゃうわ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go any further,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina won't know which direction to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:29.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドォーン！\Nええっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,撃て～！\Nシュン シュン シュン…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ おお～！\Nドカン！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:47.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カチャン(ﾌﾞﾚｰｷが外れる音)\Nええっ… ええっ!? な… 何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:49.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な な… 何～!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:02.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リタ～！ ジャンヌさ～ん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:07.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ ﾘﾀ)あっ｡\N(看守たち)ああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:18.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グッドタイミングでしょ？\N二人とも大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing, right?\NYou guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:22.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)これ このまま走り続けると\Nどこに行くのかしら？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where this leads to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:25.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)分からない｡\N私も ここまで来たことはない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never been this far either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)ニーナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふぅ…｡\N(ﾘﾀ)ちょっと 何踊ってんのよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you dancing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:53.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ いや…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(回想)((また踊ってくれるか？))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you dance with me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)ニーナ！\Nニーナ ブレーキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nina!\N-Nina, the brake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:09.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… はい！ これ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! This?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キィー…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キキィー！\Nぬぅ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:17.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボキッ！\Nああっ う… うそ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)\Nみんな しっかりつかまっていろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:27.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ ぎゃあ～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドォーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケガはないかしら？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:47.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 私は大丈夫だ｡ ニーナは？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:49.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫ほえぇ～…｡\N(２人)あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだかと思った｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:10:00.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(看守)\Nおい！ そこで何をしている!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NWhat are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Men?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男？\Nはあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(囚人たち)おお～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is all that racket?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:12.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだよ うるせぇな｡\N(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)何かあったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(看守)待て！\N≫(看守)おい 待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop right there!\N-Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:17.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(看守)待ちやがれって言ってるだろ｡\Nあいつら…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:25.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで私たち\N応援されてるんですかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think they're cheering us on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:27.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)へっ？\N(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)さあな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage of Bahamut
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(重臣たち)おぉ…｡\N(重臣)なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So they've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来たか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ見ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:00.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻撃を開始せよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,El.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エル｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドォーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士)陛下を守れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:36.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ… ちょっと\N神 強すぎないっすか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Time-out.\NAren't these gods way too strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This light is stripping us of our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:40.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)この光が\N人の力を封印しているのだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:43.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)漆黒兵部隊は\N何やってんすかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the Onyx Soldiers doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:47.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなん相手にするの\Nヤツら 得意じゃないっすか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought handling this type of enemy\Nis their specialty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even they are no match to this light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:59.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)ヤツらでも\Nあの光には かなうまい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから逃げたんすか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why they ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪シュン シュン シュン…\N(兵士たち)うわっ ああっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, they have broken through\Nthe castle gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:30.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(上級兵)申し上げます｡\N城門を突破されました｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It will not be long before they are at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:33.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間もなく 城に来ます｡\N(重臣たち)あぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:38.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれを使う｡\N(重臣たち)あっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We will use the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:43.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お言葉ながら 陛下\Nあれは 開発途上であります｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Your Highness,\Nbut the device is still in development!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:47.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今使えば 陛下に\Nどのような事態が起きるか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is used now, there is no telling what\Nit might do or what danger it may put you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:49.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,読めませぬ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not ask for your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の意見は聞いていない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to get it ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,用意しろと言っている｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:58.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… ただいま｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At once, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I guess we should get going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:19.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて 俺らも そろそろ行くか｡\N(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)あっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kaisar, take off your iron hand.\N-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:22.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイザル 義手を外せ｡\Nなぜだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早くしろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you take it off,\Nfasten it to the lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外したら錠に固定しろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stretch out the thumb first,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:32.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは親指を伸ばせ｡ 次に中指だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,then the middle finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:38.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 何をする気だ？\N何って ここから逃げ出すんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?\NWe're escaping of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:42.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は親指を曲げて\N人さし指と小指を伸ばせ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, bend the thumb and stretch out\Nthe index and pinkie fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now, get as far away from it\Nas you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:53.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし！\Nそこから できるだけ離れろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ｡\N(看守)おい！ 何をしている!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry up and step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く！ 早くしろ！\Nくっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:06.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パディオシュプロースティナズｨカ\Nカティドーレ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカン！\N(看守)うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんて顔してやがんの｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll make you a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっといいの作ってやっから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで のびてるヤツの鍵で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you grab that guy's keys\Nand unlock this cell for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:25.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちの扉も開けてくれねぇか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:29.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふふん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like my next hand to be\None that won't explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:32.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の義手は爆発しないのを頼む｡\Nへへっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't me, Rita was the one who built that in\Nbecause she was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありゃ俺じゃなくて\Nリタが仕込んだんだ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:37.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前を心配してな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She was worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:41.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心配してって… 爆発しただろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,止まれ！\N(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ ﾌｧﾊﾞﾛ)んん～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バキッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:58.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？ 今の音｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ みんな いなくなっちゃった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:06.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)行くわよ｡\Nあっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)リタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Jeanne!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌ様！\Nカイザル｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaisar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ～ すご～い！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bit more developed now,\Naren't you, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Jeanne,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaisar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am glad to see you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys know we don't\Nhave time for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay\NI cast the usual spell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stagnation, stagnation\NMy words and heart are at odds
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Default\NI've taken all the paint
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:03.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでいるの？ やった～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And mixed up all the colors\NUntil you're left with me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:06.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふん｡ ちったぁ女らしくなったか？\Nニーナ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:08.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっ！\Nぐっ！ ああ～ いってぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So fragile\NYet strong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:10.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何見てんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to overflowing\NBut not spilling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:14.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌ様 よくぞ ご無事で｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm incomplete\NI won't amount to much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイザル そなたこそ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a good luck charm\NI'm not asking for your help
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a good luck charm\NI was just clinging to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:25.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたたち そんなこと\Nやってる場合じゃないんだけど｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end it all today
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:28.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！\Nうう～ な… 何？ これ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done living this pointless life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end it all today
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やべぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken my last, pointless breath
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To whom it may concern, see ya and goodbye\NI killed the person I was yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To whom it may concern, see ya and goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)わあ～！\Nええ～!?
